{"about_the_game":"Originally released in 1999 for the Playstation, <i>Actua Ice Hockey 2</i> built upon its predecessor, sporting the same great staples of the Actua Sports series: fully 3d environments, multiple cameras, motion captured player movements, and world-class commentary.<br><br>Play in the fictional GHL (Gremlin Hockey League), at 3 speeds of play, from authentic to frantic. Manage your team, including trading players and changing tactics.<br><br>Select lines of play, change tactics on the fly, and experience bone-crunching injuries simulated in real-time, with innovative (at the time) full limb to limb collision detection.<br><br><br>This enhanced version introduces a number of modern features to this retro classic, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Saving/loading the game at any point<br></li><li> Support for most modern game controllers<br></li><li> Full control remapping<br></li><li> Image scaling and smoothing options</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1669798037","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1669798037","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152720/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1669798037","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152720/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1669798037","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":